%% Observability Stack Architecture

graph TB
    subgraph Application Layer
        Backend[⚙️ Backend Pods]
        Frontend[🎨 Frontend Pods]
    end
    
    subgraph Metrics Pipeline
        Backend -->|/metrics| PromScrape[Prometheus<br/>Scrape]
        Frontend -->|/metrics| PromScrape
        PromScrape -->|Store| Prometheus[📊 Prometheus<br/>15d Retention]
        Prometheus -->|Query| Grafana[📈 Grafana<br/>Dashboards]
        Prometheus -->|Alerts| Alertmanager[🚨 Alertmanager]
        
        Prometheus -.->|Optional<br/>Long-term| Mimir[☁️ Mimir/Thanos<br/>Central Storage]
    end
    
    subgraph Logs Pipeline
        Backend -->|stdout/stderr| Promtail[Promtail<br/>Agent]
        Frontend -->|stdout/stderr| Promtail
        Promtail -->|Push| Loki[📝 Loki<br/>30d Retention]
        Loki -->|Query| Grafana
    end
    
    subgraph Traces Pipeline
        Backend -->|OTLP| OTelCollector[OpenTelemetry<br/>Collector]
        Frontend -->|OTLP| OTelCollector
        OTelCollector -->|Store| Tempo[🔍 Tempo<br/>3d Retention]
        Tempo -->|Query| Grafana
        
        Tempo -.->|Exemplars| Prometheus
    end
    
    subgraph Alerting
        Alertmanager -->|Route| PagerDuty[📟 PagerDuty<br/>Critical]
        Alertmanager -->|Route| Slack[💬 Slack<br/>Warning]
        Alertmanager -->|Route| Email[📧 Email<br/>Info]
    end
    
    subgraph Dashboards
        Grafana -->|SLO Burn Rate| Dashboard1[📊 SLO Dashboard]
        Grafana -->|Golden Signals| Dashboard2[📊 RED Dashboard]
        Grafana -->|Business| Dashboard3[📊 Orgs/Projects]
    end
    
    %% Correlation
    Grafana -.->|Trace ID| Tempo
    Grafana -.->|Trace ID| Loki
    Loki -.->|Trace ID| Tempo
    
